==Translingual==
===Etymology===
{{L.}} [[papilio]], butterfly

===Proper noun===
'''''Papilionoideae'''''
#{{botany}} a [[botanical name]] of a [[subfamily]], within the family ''Leguminosae''. The [[circumscription]] of this group will be the same as that of 
:* family ''[[Papilionaceae]]'' (when the group is treated at the rank of family)
:* subfamily ''[[Faboideae]]'' in the family ''[[Fabaceae]]'' (when the name ''Fabaceae'' is used for the family, rather than ''Leguminosae''). 

